tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE waste_management_feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  rating INT
)

CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT, 
  feedback_text TEXT, 
  feedback_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE WasteManagementServices (
  service_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  service_type VARCHAR(50),
  service_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE ServiceQualityImprovement (
  improvement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  feedback_id INT,
  improvement_plan TEXT,
  implementation_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedbackAnalysis (
  analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  analysis_date DATE,
  feedback_id INT,
  analysis_result TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE WasteManagementCustomers (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50),
    address VARCHAR(100),
    contact_number VARCHAR(15),
    email VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE Feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    feedback_date DATE,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    rating INT
)

CREATE TABLE Services (
    service_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    service_name VARCHAR(50),
    service_description TEXT,
    service_fee DECIMAL(10, 2)
)

CREATE TABLE ServiceProviders (
    provider_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    provider_name VARCHAR(50),
    provider_type VARCHAR(50),
    provider_location VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE FeedbackAnalysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    feedback_id INT,
    analysis_date DATE,
    analysis_result TEXT
)
